WEBVTT

00:14.100 --> 00:15.940
[Grass Cottage]

00:19.120 --> 00:19.810
Come.

00:27.230 --> 00:29.250
Winter is around the corner.

00:29.730 --> 00:31.030
I wonder if during the New Year,

00:31.030 --> 00:33.000
we'll be able to see Changyu.

00:33.710 --> 00:35.350
You old woman.

00:35.880 --> 00:37.520
You're so short-sighted.

00:37.960 --> 00:41.000
Changyu is out there doing big things.

00:41.150 --> 00:43.710
How could she think about
coming home for the New Year?

00:43.710 --> 00:45.030
You old man.

00:45.060 --> 00:46.670
You just went out to fight a war.

00:46.670 --> 00:48.790
How much broader is your vision than mine?

00:48.790 --> 00:50.280
You'd be surprised.

00:50.350 --> 00:52.030
I saw more horses on this trip

00:52.030 --> 00:53.710
than the steamed buns you've eaten.

00:53.710 --> 00:55.750
My horizons have truly broadened.

00:55.750 --> 00:57.150
Weren't you just a groom?

00:57.150 --> 00:58.470
Of course you saw horses.

00:58.470 --> 01:00.470
-What else could you see?
-Who is it?

01:13.770 --> 01:17.440
[Grass Cottage]

01:15.310 --> 01:15.970
Changning!

01:16.000 --> 01:16.590
Hurry up!

01:16.930 --> 01:17.760
-Hurry!
-Go inside.

01:17.760 --> 01:18.950
-Hurry!
-Come in! Let's go!

01:18.950 --> 01:19.710
Hurry!

01:21.410 --> 01:22.340
Hurry! This way!

01:24.840 --> 01:25.610
Hide!

02:31.360 --> 02:32.150
Qi?

02:33.560 --> 02:34.430
Qi?

02:38.680 --> 02:39.810
Mr. Zhao, Mrs. Zhao.

02:39.870 --> 02:41.130
It's safe outside now.

02:41.280 --> 02:42.400
Really?

02:47.480 --> 02:48.610
Where is Manager Yu?

02:50.800 --> 02:51.630
Manager Yu?

02:51.910 --> 02:52.360
Manager Yu!

02:52.360 --> 02:52.960
Bao'er!

02:53.030 --> 02:53.590
Bao'er!

04:26.050 --> 04:31.390
[Pursuit of Jade]

04:31.470 --> 04:34.150
[Episode 35]

04:38.510 --> 04:41.040
You said she held a knife to her neck,

04:41.040 --> 04:43.170
threatening you to release Yu Bao'er?

04:43.360 --> 04:43.950
Yes.

04:45.120 --> 04:46.510
Cut off the arm

04:46.530 --> 04:47.970
he used to slash her with.

04:48.680 --> 04:50.480
If Her Ladyship doesn't wake up,

04:50.480 --> 04:51.920
you will be buried with her.

04:51.920 --> 04:53.780
Thank you for your grace, Master.

05:03.720 --> 05:04.600
You're awake?

05:09.610 --> 05:11.140
You two doctors, come here.

05:16.870 --> 05:18.130
Save her immediately.

05:18.190 --> 05:19.720
If anything happens to her,

05:20.160 --> 05:22.070
none of you will live.

05:22.450 --> 05:23.720
She suffered a knife wound.

05:23.720 --> 05:26.680
The wound reopened,
causing a persistent high fever.

05:26.680 --> 05:28.040
Then find a solution!

05:28.360 --> 05:29.310
Yes, yes.

05:29.310 --> 05:30.910
Right away. We'll find a way.

05:31.830 --> 05:33.430
Don't kill innocent people.

05:34.310 --> 05:35.750
If you kill them,

05:36.830 --> 05:38.730
I won't live either.

05:40.950 --> 05:42.000
You can't die.

05:42.560 --> 05:43.890
As long as you're alive,

05:44.159 --> 05:45.760
I will promise you anything.

05:50.800 --> 05:51.630
Qianqian.

05:53.310 --> 05:54.070
Qianqian?

05:55.630 --> 05:57.360
Find all the doctors within 100 li

05:57.360 --> 05:58.490
and bring them here!

06:02.600 --> 06:03.120
You!

06:11.360 --> 06:12.160
Next one!

06:13.200 --> 06:13.810
Get in!

06:16.350 --> 06:17.160
Next!

06:19.520 --> 06:20.290
Spare me!

06:20.360 --> 06:20.950
You!

06:21.920 --> 06:23.380
-Please spare me!
-Get in!

06:23.750 --> 06:24.360
And you!

06:33.720 --> 06:35.290
Sh-she's awake.

06:35.680 --> 06:36.480
She's awake.

06:37.630 --> 06:38.390
Qianqian.

06:46.040 --> 06:47.300
You're finally awake.

07:02.400 --> 07:05.060
Didn't you promise me
you wouldn't kill anyone?

07:06.250 --> 07:07.420
How could you...

07:12.000 --> 07:12.630
Guards.

07:13.310 --> 07:13.920
Yes.

07:14.560 --> 07:15.430
Wake them up.

07:15.870 --> 07:16.480
Yes!

07:20.190 --> 07:20.750
Get up!

07:21.630 --> 07:22.240
Get up!

07:24.480 --> 07:25.000
Get up!

07:25.120 --> 07:26.040
Forgive us, My Lady.

07:26.040 --> 07:27.160
We are fine.

07:27.510 --> 07:28.720
Sorry for startling you.

07:28.720 --> 07:29.390
Look.

07:30.310 --> 07:31.240
It's fake.

07:32.150 --> 07:33.830
I only knocked them out

07:34.190 --> 07:35.670
to scare them.

07:37.360 --> 07:39.220
It's just that in this backwater,

07:39.870 --> 07:41.870
if I hadn't threatened them
with their lives,

07:41.870 --> 07:43.530
how could these quack doctors

07:43.630 --> 07:45.690
have saved you with all their hearts?

07:48.540 --> 07:50.159
I remember every word

07:51.070 --> 07:52.070
you said.

07:58.250 --> 07:59.360
Take them back.

08:01.040 --> 08:01.510
Get up!

08:01.670 --> 08:02.270
Get up!

08:03.000 --> 08:03.630
Get up!

08:06.910 --> 08:07.420
Go!

08:08.070 --> 08:08.530
Hurry up!

08:08.530 --> 08:09.060
Move!

08:09.310 --> 08:09.720
Hurry!

08:13.390 --> 08:14.360
This stab wound

08:15.350 --> 08:16.960
nearly cost you your life.

08:18.680 --> 08:20.800
Why did you shield that little brat?

08:25.430 --> 08:25.950
Mother!

08:25.950 --> 08:27.450
-Useless! I told you to kill the small one!
-Mother!

08:27.450 --> 08:28.980
But you slashed the big one!

08:30.480 --> 08:31.190
Don't move!

08:31.390 --> 08:32.150
Run!

08:32.549 --> 08:34.110
Go find Uncle Xie Qi!

08:34.200 --> 08:35.030
Go!

08:35.150 --> 08:36.080
Mother!

08:36.320 --> 08:37.240
Run!

08:43.630 --> 08:45.030
If you dare release those arrows,

08:45.030 --> 08:46.090
I will kill myself!

08:46.150 --> 08:48.680
Let's see how you explain that
to that madman!

08:49.030 --> 08:51.430
Even a vicious tiger
won't eat its own cubs.

08:52.550 --> 08:54.480
You'd even kill your own son.

08:55.790 --> 08:58.250
I really don't know
why they're loyal to you.

08:59.030 --> 09:00.830
Aren't they afraid that one day,

09:01.750 --> 09:02.950
you'll kill them too?

09:04.670 --> 09:05.720
After all,

09:06.840 --> 09:09.440
you're just angry
that I wanted to kill Yu Bao'er.

09:09.440 --> 09:10.510
You're smart.

09:11.440 --> 09:12.600
You must know

09:12.670 --> 09:15.530
that Xie Zheng could use him
to command the vassals.

09:22.320 --> 09:24.200
This child came at a bad time.

09:26.200 --> 09:27.550
Take care of yourself.

09:28.360 --> 09:29.690
Once I ascend the throne

09:29.840 --> 09:31.300
and rule over all the land,

09:31.510 --> 09:33.830
we can have as many children

09:34.030 --> 09:35.360
as you wish.

09:41.910 --> 09:42.510
Oh, right.

09:43.440 --> 09:45.200
I have a surprise for you.

09:47.510 --> 09:48.200
Come in.

09:52.080 --> 09:52.870
My Lady.

09:55.030 --> 09:56.030
Zisu?

09:56.630 --> 09:57.630
You're alive?

09:58.000 --> 09:59.000
Thank goodness.

09:59.000 --> 10:00.490
You're finally awake.

10:01.080 --> 10:01.790
Look.

10:02.200 --> 10:04.150
I found the maid

10:04.200 --> 10:05.600
who serves you best back.

10:06.030 --> 10:06.870
With her here,

10:07.000 --> 10:08.800
you're sure to recover quickly.

10:36.240 --> 10:36.960
Changyu.

10:37.200 --> 10:37.790
Are you getting used to living

10:37.790 --> 10:39.080
in the General's Mansion?

10:39.080 --> 10:40.070
I am.

10:40.200 --> 10:41.480
There just aren't many people.

10:41.480 --> 10:42.790
It's not lively enough.

10:42.790 --> 10:44.790
I've never lived in such a big house.

10:45.150 --> 10:46.790
Even my voice echoes.

10:46.870 --> 10:47.910
To be honest,

10:48.240 --> 10:50.370
I'm scared to call for anyone at night.

10:50.440 --> 10:51.790
It's quite spooky.

10:53.790 --> 10:55.320
Beholden... no.

10:56.440 --> 10:57.300
Your Highness.

10:57.600 --> 10:58.750
Why so formal?

10:58.750 --> 11:01.210
I still prefer you calling me
Miss Beholden.

11:01.870 --> 11:02.440
By the way,

11:02.440 --> 11:03.840
I have something for you.

11:16.320 --> 11:17.390
Here, open it.

11:21.600 --> 11:22.600
I chose all these clothes

11:22.600 --> 11:24.270
especially for you.

11:25.840 --> 11:27.100
And some jewelry, too.

11:28.270 --> 11:29.080
Keep them.

11:29.080 --> 11:29.840
Wear them when you're off duty.

11:29.840 --> 11:31.390
Even though you're a great general now,

11:31.390 --> 11:32.870
you should still be a pretty young lady.

11:32.870 --> 11:34.480
But this is too much.

11:34.480 --> 11:35.630
And they're too expensive.

11:35.630 --> 11:36.390
Between us,

11:36.390 --> 11:38.520
there's no need for such formalities.

11:38.670 --> 11:39.270
Try this on.

11:39.270 --> 11:40.840
The one I'm wearing is fine.

11:40.840 --> 11:43.970
-Try it on. It's beautiful.
-This one is not bad, really.

11:44.080 --> 11:45.030
Let's not do this now.

11:45.030 --> 11:46.030
Come on, just try it!

11:46.030 --> 11:47.030
I'm not changing. Really!

11:47.030 --> 11:47.560
Changyu!

11:48.270 --> 11:50.670
-Try it. You will look pretty!
-I'm not used to wearing this kind of clothes.

11:50.670 --> 11:51.600
Listen to me!

11:57.070 --> 11:57.970
So beautiful.

11:58.240 --> 11:58.870
Let me see.

12:07.130 --> 12:08.750
Our Flower-Crowned General

12:08.880 --> 12:10.770
is so beautiful.

12:10.910 --> 12:12.910
Marquis of Wu'an is really blessed.

12:14.960 --> 12:16.430
Your Highness. General.

12:17.910 --> 12:19.750
The officials of the Ministry of Rites
will come

12:19.750 --> 12:22.150
to teach you the palace etiquette
in 2 days.

12:22.390 --> 12:23.150
What?

12:24.340 --> 12:27.770
[Department of Rites]

12:32.080 --> 12:34.210
You're just standing there like a log!

12:34.320 --> 12:35.250
Such a nuisance.

12:36.480 --> 12:38.080
Why are you so rude?

12:38.150 --> 12:40.280
It was clearly you who bumped into him!

12:41.270 --> 12:42.870
What does it have to do with you?

12:42.870 --> 12:43.270
You...

12:43.270 --> 12:44.000
Wu.

12:44.720 --> 12:47.030
Forget it. Let's not make trouble.

12:49.940 --> 12:51.630
Thank you for speaking up, Wu.

12:54.200 --> 12:55.960
We've been stuck here doing chores

12:55.960 --> 12:56.960
for almost a year.

12:57.750 --> 13:00.350
Who knows when His Majesty
will have use for us?

13:01.120 --> 13:02.240
I've almost lost

13:02.240 --> 13:03.840
track of time.

13:08.320 --> 13:09.120
Yes.

13:11.480 --> 13:13.340
I've almost forgotten what color

13:14.930 --> 13:16.330
the sky in the Capital is.

13:17.960 --> 13:19.490
Song, you are a scholar too.

13:20.000 --> 13:22.360
Why must you endure their bullying?

13:27.390 --> 13:28.850
My mother has passed away.

13:29.240 --> 13:31.150
I have no kin left to support me.

13:32.360 --> 13:35.120
The cost of living in the Capital

13:35.240 --> 13:36.440
costs a fortune.

13:37.200 --> 13:38.660
If I don't swallow my pride

13:39.200 --> 13:41.360
and lose this hard-earned salary,

13:42.670 --> 13:44.630
I will end up on the streets.

13:46.030 --> 13:47.830
I'll just endure it a bit longer.

13:48.790 --> 13:50.200
My day will come.

13:57.790 --> 13:59.120
Back in Lin'an,

13:59.870 --> 14:01.240
after I passed the provincial exam,

14:01.240 --> 14:02.790
I was praised by everyone.

14:04.960 --> 14:06.840
I thought I was one of a kind.

14:07.480 --> 14:08.740
But now in the Capital,

14:08.960 --> 14:11.160
I realize dignitaries are everywhere.

14:11.840 --> 14:13.390
Throw a wine jar,

14:14.000 --> 14:15.600
and you'll hit a few scholars like me,

14:15.600 --> 14:17.400
whose talents go unrecognized.

14:18.960 --> 14:20.690
It really confirms the saying,

14:22.720 --> 14:23.840
"when the northern geese fly south..."

14:23.840 --> 14:25.360
"When the northern geese fly south,

14:25.360 --> 14:28.790
the phoenixes won't be able find
a place to land."

14:28.960 --> 14:30.030
Well said!

14:30.750 --> 14:32.630
"When the northern geese fly south,

14:32.630 --> 14:35.240
the phoenixes won't be able find
a place to land."

14:35.240 --> 14:36.630
Song, you are overflowing with talent.

14:36.630 --> 14:38.630
You will surely achieve greatness.

14:41.630 --> 14:42.320
Song.

14:42.750 --> 14:43.390
Song!

14:43.440 --> 14:44.630
Lord Liu, Chief Official
of the Ministry of Rites,

14:44.630 --> 14:45.630
has a note for you.

14:53.870 --> 14:57.600
There's a newly appointed
Flower-Crowned General in the Capital.

14:59.000 --> 15:00.440
Lord Liu wants me to teach the General

15:00.440 --> 15:01.720
court etiquette?

15:02.200 --> 15:04.870
That Flower-Crowned General
is a fourth-rank official.

15:04.870 --> 15:06.200
Teaching etiquette to a high official

15:06.200 --> 15:07.510
is a lucrative job.

15:07.910 --> 15:09.240
I didn't expect Lord Liu

15:09.440 --> 15:11.240
to appreciate you so much, Song.

15:12.390 --> 15:14.630
But I heard this female general

15:14.910 --> 15:16.480
used to be a peasant.

15:16.720 --> 15:18.320
She is crude, unreasonable,

15:18.360 --> 15:19.840
and unfit for high society.

15:19.840 --> 15:21.910
Song's talent is unmatched in the Capital.

15:21.910 --> 15:23.360
This assignment

15:23.790 --> 15:25.480
is a waste of your talent.

15:25.750 --> 15:26.840
You flatter me, Wu.

15:27.480 --> 15:30.910
Confucius said, "In education
there should be no class distinction."

15:30.910 --> 15:33.840
If Flower-Crowned General
sincerely wants to learn etiquette,

15:33.840 --> 15:35.150
I am willing

15:36.080 --> 15:37.270
to do my humble best.

15:40.510 --> 15:42.240
Please have some tea, My Lords.

15:43.080 --> 15:44.080
Please, Lord Liu.

15:45.240 --> 15:45.870
Please.

15:53.790 --> 15:55.320
Greetings, General.

15:56.670 --> 15:57.510
General,

15:58.000 --> 15:59.060
I'm Song Yan,
clerk of the Ministry of Rites.

15:59.060 --> 16:00.120
By imperial order,

16:00.150 --> 16:03.550
I'm here to explain the essentials
of court etiquette to you.

16:13.320 --> 16:14.890
General.

16:15.080 --> 16:17.930
Clerk Song is well-versed in etiquette.

16:18.270 --> 16:19.240
He is surely up to...

16:19.240 --> 16:21.360
How big an official is Clerk Song?

16:22.240 --> 16:23.320
General,

16:23.840 --> 16:25.900
junior ninth-rank.

16:26.270 --> 16:26.870
However...

16:26.870 --> 16:28.200
-Fan Changyu?
-Song...

16:29.270 --> 16:30.840
You are the Flower-Crowned General?

16:30.840 --> 16:31.710
Audacious!

16:32.030 --> 16:34.290
How dare you call the General by her name!

16:34.320 --> 16:36.450
And you're from the Ministry of Rites.

16:37.080 --> 16:38.170
Long time no see,

16:38.600 --> 16:39.390
Song Yan.

16:43.270 --> 16:46.630
So General and Scholar Song
are old acquaintances.

16:46.790 --> 16:48.080
That is wonderful.

16:48.510 --> 16:50.840
I don't deserve the term "acquaintance."

16:55.000 --> 16:55.750
Changyu...

16:59.030 --> 17:00.630
General, I will never forget

17:01.200 --> 17:02.600
your family's kindness.

17:03.150 --> 17:03.910
Regarding what happened back then...

17:03.910 --> 17:05.109
According to the law,

17:05.200 --> 17:06.510
scholars

17:06.720 --> 17:08.319
need not kneel to officials.

17:08.349 --> 17:09.550
Help Scholar Song up.

17:09.750 --> 17:10.400
Yes!

17:18.790 --> 17:21.589
The money my father paid
for the coffin and tuition,

17:21.589 --> 17:22.990
you have already repaid.

17:23.310 --> 17:24.510
We are even.

17:26.400 --> 17:27.829
There is no such thing as

17:28.270 --> 17:30.000
the "kindness" you mentioned.

17:33.830 --> 17:34.590
Yes.

17:34.920 --> 17:36.580
But congratulations anyway.

17:36.720 --> 17:37.880
You got your wish.

17:38.100 --> 17:39.690
Junior ninth-rank?

17:42.030 --> 17:43.270
That counts as an official.

17:43.270 --> 17:45.160
Your mother can rest in peace.

17:46.200 --> 17:46.730
Alright.

17:47.200 --> 17:48.720
You know I won't use you.

17:48.790 --> 17:49.440
Go now.

17:50.240 --> 17:51.750
We will take our leave.

17:53.400 --> 17:54.750
Let's go. Hurry up.

17:59.880 --> 18:01.180
Come here. Come here.

18:02.000 --> 18:03.050
Between you and the General,

18:03.050 --> 18:04.570
what exactly happened?

18:06.160 --> 18:07.270
We used to...

18:08.480 --> 18:09.700
It's a long story.

18:09.830 --> 18:11.400
Then make it short.

18:11.510 --> 18:13.000
Why didn't you tell me sooner

18:13.000 --> 18:15.070
that you had such a history
with the General?

18:15.070 --> 18:16.830
You almost got me killed, you know that?

18:16.830 --> 18:18.440
Isn't this Scholar Song?

18:18.690 --> 18:25.390
[Where Clouds Roam and Snow Dances]

18:19.480 --> 18:20.270
Guard Jin.

18:21.590 --> 18:25.070
Scholar Song is such a big official now.

18:25.480 --> 18:27.410
Where are you going, Scholar Song?

18:28.030 --> 18:29.300
Let me see you off.

18:30.070 --> 18:30.750
Guard Jin!

18:30.570 --> 18:32.330
[Where Clouds Roam and Snow Dances]

18:31.510 --> 18:32.000
Guard Jin!

18:32.000 --> 18:33.000
I'll go by myself.

18:34.640 --> 18:35.240
Guard Jin.

18:35.310 --> 18:37.750
-You... You can't do this.
-How dare you hit an official!

18:37.750 --> 18:39.160
It's a misunderstanding.

18:39.160 --> 18:41.350
I am a dignified
seventh-rank Imperial Guard.

18:41.350 --> 18:42.720
I was just kindly seeing you off.

18:42.720 --> 18:44.920
How did this
turn into beating an official?

18:44.920 --> 18:47.450
Besides, your boss
hasn't said anything yet.

18:47.720 --> 18:48.650
Right, Lord Liu?

18:50.680 --> 18:51.350
Yes, yes.

18:51.370 --> 18:52.590
Guard Jin, you're right.

18:52.590 --> 18:53.990
He... he fell by himself.

18:54.350 --> 18:56.480
You are abusing your power
for personal revenge!

18:56.480 --> 18:58.740
Abusing our power
for personal revenge?

18:58.880 --> 18:59.830
So what?

19:01.830 --> 19:03.030
Back in the village,

19:03.590 --> 19:05.120
weren't you very arrogant?

19:05.590 --> 19:07.190
You even bullied our sister.

19:09.030 --> 19:10.190
-Now...
-You...

19:10.350 --> 19:12.200
You aren't even fit to serve her.

19:12.350 --> 19:13.000
Exactly!

19:13.000 --> 19:13.510
You!

19:15.240 --> 19:17.500
I know the General is now of noble status,

19:18.000 --> 19:20.460
and I know I'm not worthy
to mention the past.

19:21.930 --> 19:23.620
I just hope you remember

19:25.160 --> 19:27.420
that my original intention and ambition

19:27.550 --> 19:28.630
have never changed!

19:28.630 --> 19:29.760
Let's go!

19:29.790 --> 19:31.520
Do you want to get beaten again?

19:31.680 --> 19:33.200
What kind of unforgivable sin
did you commit?

19:33.200 --> 19:35.000
You offended everyone
in the General's Mansion?

19:33.370 --> 19:34.680
[Where Clouds Roam and Snow Dances]

19:35.000 --> 19:36.310
-See if I can scare you to death.
-Tell me!

19:36.310 --> 19:37.170
What did you do?

19:37.640 --> 19:38.270
Tell me.

19:57.790 --> 19:59.190
The matrilocal husband?

20:00.440 --> 20:02.740
Fan Changyu didn't abandon you,
her matrilocal husband?

20:02.740 --> 20:06.160
Instead, she made you climb up the ladder
and enjoy a luxurious life!

20:06.160 --> 20:09.890
-What exactly do I lack compared to...
-What are you talking about?

20:10.200 --> 20:11.400
Your Lordship! Your Lordship!

20:11.400 --> 20:13.030
Please don't lower yourself to his level.

20:13.030 --> 20:14.070
Your Lordship. Your Lordship.

20:14.070 --> 20:15.960
Wh-why are you here?

20:17.440 --> 20:18.750
You saw me returning to the Capital

20:18.750 --> 20:20.280
without an imperial edict.

20:21.270 --> 20:23.130
If you report this to His Majesty,

20:24.070 --> 20:26.310
you could trade it
for a lifetime of wealth and glory.

20:26.310 --> 20:27.240
Your Lordship,

20:27.350 --> 20:29.110
I wouldn't dare!

20:29.200 --> 20:30.480
I didn't see anything!

20:30.590 --> 20:32.430
I saw nothing, Your Lordship.

20:33.750 --> 20:35.070
What are you standing there for?

20:35.070 --> 20:37.550
Hurry up and pay your respects
to the Marquis of Wu'an!

20:37.550 --> 20:39.270
Your Lordship,
he didn't see anything either.

20:39.270 --> 20:41.020
Neither of us saw anything!

20:42.960 --> 20:44.170
The Marquis of Wu'an?

20:50.510 --> 20:51.400
Look up.

21:07.750 --> 21:09.680
"When the northern geese fly south,

21:09.680 --> 21:12.410
the phoenixes won't be able find
a place to land."

21:17.960 --> 21:19.440
Well, Your Lordship...

21:20.400 --> 21:21.440
Who is this?

21:21.790 --> 21:23.000
He's so frail.

21:23.510 --> 21:25.000
A petty clerk from the Ministry of Rites.

21:25.000 --> 21:26.590
He hasn't seen much of the world.

21:26.590 --> 21:27.780
Maybe just now,

21:27.830 --> 21:29.750
he was scared into fainting
by your presence.

21:29.750 --> 21:32.150
Your Lordship, please don't take offense.

21:34.550 --> 21:35.660
His Lordship asked you

21:35.660 --> 21:38.390
to spread the word
about him being in the Capital.

21:40.310 --> 21:41.440
Did you understand?

21:43.830 --> 21:45.240
I... I wouldn't dare.

21:45.270 --> 21:46.880
I... I swear on my life.

21:46.880 --> 21:48.720
His Lordship can rest assured.

21:48.720 --> 21:50.590
If there's even a whisper of gossip

21:50.590 --> 21:52.270
floating above the Capital,

21:52.270 --> 21:53.580
-you can hold me responsible.
-You really didn't understand.

21:53.580 --> 21:54.790
You can hold me responsible.

21:54.790 --> 21:55.400
Really.

21:55.590 --> 21:56.590
I swear on my life.

22:05.790 --> 22:07.160
Why are you crying?

22:07.240 --> 22:08.890
I should be the one crying!

22:09.070 --> 22:10.190
Get up!

22:10.680 --> 22:12.590
What kind of bad luck
from eight lifetimes have I had

22:12.410 --> 22:19.790
[Where Clouds Roam and Snow Dances]

22:12.610 --> 22:14.710
to bring a jinx like you here?

22:15.070 --> 22:15.970
Let's go!

22:16.070 --> 22:17.390
It's so embarrassing!

22:29.830 --> 22:31.760
You came out with me just like this?

22:32.350 --> 22:34.150
Aren't you afraid of being seen?

22:36.200 --> 22:38.860
I promised to show you
the beauty of the Capital.

22:39.110 --> 22:40.510
How could I break my word?

22:44.310 --> 22:45.000
What?

22:46.070 --> 22:47.130
Did seeing Song Yan

22:47.200 --> 22:48.330
put you in a bad mood?

22:49.750 --> 22:51.680
So you do remember him.

22:52.920 --> 22:54.450
I thought you'd forgotten.

22:54.640 --> 22:56.480
It's not that I don't remember him.

22:56.480 --> 22:58.280
I just never took him seriously.

23:06.070 --> 23:07.000
Are you jealous?

23:07.720 --> 23:09.180
Your expression changed.

23:10.000 --> 23:10.910
Ridiculous.

23:13.340 --> 23:14.600
That would be the best.

23:15.110 --> 23:17.370
Otherwise, you'd be lowering yourself.

23:17.750 --> 23:19.400
I remember back in Lin'an,

23:19.440 --> 23:20.270
I said

23:20.350 --> 23:21.790
that when you become a high official

23:21.790 --> 23:22.830
and meet Song Yan again,

23:22.830 --> 23:25.430
you should teach him a lesson for me
as revenge.

23:27.920 --> 23:28.680
Sure.

23:28.960 --> 23:30.830
It's not too late to do that now.

23:31.830 --> 23:32.720
Stop the carriage.

23:32.720 --> 23:33.430
No.

23:34.110 --> 23:36.230
That's not what I meant.

23:36.350 --> 23:37.410
Does a mere Song Yan

23:37.480 --> 23:40.480
really need the Marquis of Wu'an
to teach him a lesson?

23:55.160 --> 23:56.760
The Capital is so beautiful.

23:57.480 --> 23:58.820
In the past,

23:59.070 --> 24:01.330
I envied Song Yan so much for coming here.

24:02.200 --> 24:03.000
What a pity.

24:03.480 --> 24:06.810
With people like Prime Minister Wei
and Grand Tutor Li here,

24:10.440 --> 24:12.240
the Capital is nothing special.

24:15.310 --> 24:16.350
Don't worry.

24:16.680 --> 24:17.880
One day,

24:18.790 --> 24:20.830
all these treacherous
and corrupt officials

24:20.830 --> 24:22.270
will be rooted out,

24:23.680 --> 24:26.000
and peace will be restored to the world.

24:43.000 --> 24:44.070
Fireworks!

24:46.070 --> 24:47.830
This way, we can stay in the carriage

24:47.830 --> 24:49.290
and watch from a distance.

24:49.350 --> 24:50.810
Why watch from a distance?

24:51.750 --> 24:52.400
Let's go.

24:53.080 --> 24:54.140
Stop the carriage.

24:59.000 --> 25:00.260
Why are we getting out?

25:01.200 --> 25:02.340
Where are we going?

25:03.000 --> 25:03.600
Follow me.

25:10.510 --> 25:11.110
Waiter.

25:11.250 --> 25:12.320
A private table for two.

25:12.320 --> 25:14.250
Alright. Come on, this way please.

25:16.530 --> 25:17.360
Look.

25:18.030 --> 25:19.260
You entered the Capital
without permission.

25:19.260 --> 25:21.390
It's a serious crime if you're caught.

25:21.510 --> 25:22.680
So what?

25:23.160 --> 25:24.490
Who dares to impeach me?

25:24.910 --> 25:26.620
Even if someone dares,

25:26.760 --> 25:29.090
would that little Emperor dare to listen?

25:32.240 --> 25:33.880
You kept telling me

25:34.350 --> 25:36.240
you wanted to tour the Capital at night.

25:36.240 --> 25:38.240
How can we just stay in the carriage?

25:41.580 --> 25:44.090
♪ The moon is as quiet as me ♪

25:44.870 --> 25:46.530
♪ The light shines ♪

25:47.170 --> 25:49.840
♪ It illuminates
the turbulence in my heart ♪

25:50.340 --> 25:52.960
♪ It seems to be the fire of love ♪

25:53.520 --> 25:55.320
♪ Just a few sparks ♪

25:55.780 --> 26:00.610
♪ Let me hide in your heart ♪

25:58.160 --> 25:59.320
Actually,

26:00.400 --> 26:02.960
I'm especially grateful
to Song Yan for one thing.

26:02.960 --> 26:04.270
Song Yan? What is it?

26:03.080 --> 26:04.320
♪ I pray that our love ♪

26:04.340 --> 26:06.880
♪ Will never end ♪

26:05.240 --> 26:06.770
I thank Song Yan

26:06.920 --> 26:08.720
for not appreciating Fan Changyu.

26:07.510 --> 26:08.680
♪ It's worth my foolishly waiting ♪

26:08.700 --> 26:10.950
♪ For a lifetime ♪

26:11.720 --> 26:15.640
♪ Clear and quiet as me ♪

26:15.930 --> 26:19.760
♪ So what if we encounter difficulties? ♪

26:16.880 --> 26:18.070
You once said

26:18.830 --> 26:20.290
that I, an uncovered jade,

26:20.420 --> 26:21.310
♪ I pray that our love ♪

26:20.790 --> 26:23.000
don't belong to you
even if your name is carved on me.

26:21.330 --> 26:23.930
♪ Will not be like sand
slipping into the sea ♪

26:24.480 --> 26:26.110
But now I know...

26:25.230 --> 26:26.240
♪ I'd rather use this life ♪

26:26.270 --> 26:28.630
♪ To guard our love forever ♪

26:28.070 --> 26:29.440
you are the jade.

26:29.210 --> 26:33.370
♪ Clear and quiet as me ♪

26:33.750 --> 26:41.990
♪ Why do we need
to seek cause and effect ♪

26:54.960 --> 26:57.480
Your Highness, you've had a long journey
back to the Capital.

26:57.480 --> 26:59.830
This is the Li family's private residence.

26:59.830 --> 27:01.830
You can stay here with peace of mind.

27:02.960 --> 27:04.290
I have sent men

27:04.590 --> 27:07.120
to closely monitor
Fan Changyu's residence.

27:07.160 --> 27:09.020
We will follow the clues

27:09.480 --> 27:10.960
to convict Xie Zheng

27:11.070 --> 27:14.270
of treason for returning to the Capital
without an edict.

27:16.270 --> 27:17.350
Grand Tutor Li,

27:17.510 --> 27:20.310
it would be better to have that
foolish Emperor issue a decree,

27:20.310 --> 27:21.840
openly summoning Xie Zheng

27:22.160 --> 27:25.030
to bring his grand army back to court
for rewards.

27:27.110 --> 27:28.710
What do you mean?

27:29.070 --> 27:30.640
Among the war prisoners from Chongzhou,

27:30.640 --> 27:32.440
there are many of my trusted men.

27:33.200 --> 27:35.270
They have now infiltrated the Yanzhou Army

27:35.270 --> 27:37.130
that is returning to the Capital.

27:37.720 --> 27:38.830
Lord Changxin

27:39.110 --> 27:41.720
coveted the Capital of Great Yin
all his life.

27:42.070 --> 27:43.350
But he never expected

27:43.680 --> 27:45.680
that I could use Xie Zheng

27:46.450 --> 27:47.610
to bring the rebel troops

27:47.610 --> 27:49.760
openly into the Capital.

27:49.790 --> 27:52.070
Only with an army can one win.

27:55.480 --> 27:59.320
Your Highness,
you're indeed of royal blood.

27:59.640 --> 28:02.070
Your wisdom and methods are superior.

28:02.590 --> 28:05.750
I am willing to serve you faithfully

28:06.200 --> 28:08.960
to achieve your great cause soon.

28:22.070 --> 28:24.710
[Shaking Heaven and Earth]

28:26.110 --> 28:26.970
Close the door.

28:30.960 --> 28:32.420
I heard you're returning to the Capital
on orders.

28:32.420 --> 28:33.330
Yes.

28:34.200 --> 28:35.600
They know I've returned,

28:36.110 --> 28:38.770
so they had His Majesty
summon me to the Capital.

28:39.720 --> 28:42.070
Also, the falcon brought news.

28:42.960 --> 28:45.470
Qi Min used all his Suicide Warriors

28:45.500 --> 28:46.900
and captured Manager Yu.

28:48.880 --> 28:49.680
Damn it.

28:50.030 --> 28:50.880
I'll bring Qianqian back.

28:50.880 --> 28:51.350
Wait.

28:51.920 --> 28:52.680
Don't rush.

28:53.270 --> 28:55.270
I've already sent men to rescue her.

28:56.720 --> 28:57.720
For this matter,

28:58.590 --> 28:59.790
we need to find another way.

28:59.790 --> 29:00.920
Find what way?

29:01.480 --> 29:03.240
That Qi is a mad dog.

29:03.400 --> 29:05.600
When he goes mad, he even bites himself.

29:05.830 --> 29:07.400
Qi Min looks vicious,

29:07.680 --> 29:10.030
but he's actually devoted to Manager Yu.

29:10.310 --> 29:12.240
He won't have the heart to kill her.

29:16.110 --> 29:16.920
Sister.

29:17.480 --> 29:17.960
Sister!

29:17.960 --> 29:19.160
Bad news!

29:19.510 --> 29:20.830
Rumor has it

29:20.830 --> 29:23.490
the Emperor wants to make you
his Noble Consort!

29:29.000 --> 29:30.400
I've said before

29:30.830 --> 29:32.350
that I'm already married.

29:32.400 --> 29:33.310
Exactly.

29:33.440 --> 29:34.720
Who would give up being a general

29:34.720 --> 29:35.920
just to be someone's concubine?

29:35.920 --> 29:36.400
Would you?

29:36.400 --> 29:37.640
It's utter nonsense.

29:37.790 --> 29:40.160
The Flower-Crowned General's fame
has already spread throughout the Capital.

29:40.160 --> 29:42.020
She has the people's support now.

29:42.480 --> 29:43.920
His Majesty is doing this

29:44.030 --> 29:45.680
to borrow the General's power

29:45.680 --> 29:48.210
to counter the powerful ministers
Wei and Li.

29:48.960 --> 29:50.000
Yes.

29:50.240 --> 29:51.920
They're here to sound you out.

29:53.350 --> 29:54.070
Do you fancy it?

29:54.070 --> 29:54.790
Bah!

29:55.880 --> 29:57.750
To think I used to pity him.

29:58.400 --> 30:00.070
If he dares to lay his pig trotters on me,

30:00.070 --> 30:01.640
I'll slaughter him right there.

30:01.640 --> 30:02.680
I'll show him

30:03.160 --> 30:06.760
that I didn't earn the name
Pig-Butchering General for nothing.

30:20.310 --> 30:23.380
[Match]

30:25.030 --> 30:26.400
Fan, come here.

30:29.720 --> 30:32.050
I wrote these characters
especially for you

30:32.050 --> 30:33.380
to express my feelings.

30:33.790 --> 30:34.920
See if you like them.

30:35.340 --> 30:39.190
"A fair maiden
is a gentleman's perfect match."

30:40.640 --> 30:42.040
Beautiful handwriting.

30:42.070 --> 30:44.000
It's a pity I can barely read.

30:44.770 --> 30:46.220
[Maiden] [Man]

30:44.920 --> 30:46.780
I only recognize these two words.

30:49.070 --> 30:49.830
No matter.

30:50.200 --> 30:52.000
I will explain it to you.

30:53.110 --> 30:55.110
This is a famous line
from the Book of Songs.

30:55.110 --> 30:56.830
It praises your beauty.

30:56.690 --> 30:58.210
[Act with Caution]

30:56.830 --> 30:58.400
Even I am captivated.

31:03.790 --> 31:04.550
In short,

31:04.720 --> 31:06.000
you are the most beautiful woman

31:06.000 --> 31:07.030
in Great Yin.

31:08.920 --> 31:10.590
I have no beauty.

31:11.110 --> 31:12.590
Just some brute strength.

31:12.750 --> 31:14.480
Your Majesty, you may not know,

31:14.510 --> 31:16.110
when I was in the countryside,

31:16.110 --> 31:18.310
a scholar broke off our engagement.

31:18.510 --> 31:20.480
I had to take a matrilocal husband

31:20.550 --> 31:21.860
to save face

31:21.960 --> 31:23.560
and the family butcher shop.

31:23.920 --> 31:24.720
Your Majesty,

31:25.070 --> 31:27.240
you must support women like me

31:27.260 --> 31:28.540
who have no brothers

31:28.720 --> 31:30.850
and change the Legal Code of Great Yin.

31:31.000 --> 31:32.030
We women

31:32.200 --> 31:33.750
shouldn't have to marry a man

31:33.750 --> 31:34.880
to survive.

31:35.400 --> 31:36.880
As long as we can support ourselves

31:36.880 --> 31:38.070
and pay the land tax,

31:38.960 --> 31:40.480
we should count as a household.

31:40.480 --> 31:42.030
There's no need for a male in the house.

31:42.030 --> 31:43.790
Don't you agree, Your Majesty?

31:45.270 --> 31:46.200
Fan,

31:46.440 --> 31:48.550
you've reached a high position now.

31:48.550 --> 31:50.510
Don't dwell on the past.

31:52.000 --> 31:53.070
As for amending the laws,

31:53.070 --> 31:53.960
I promise you.

31:56.030 --> 31:58.750
Because you are someone I truly cherish.

31:59.310 --> 32:02.070
On behalf of all suffering women,
I, Fan Changyu,

32:02.480 --> 32:04.410
thank Your Majesty for your grace.

32:04.790 --> 32:06.070
Please rise, F—

32:09.440 --> 32:11.070
You have quite a grip.

32:11.680 --> 32:14.030
What other hobbies do you have?

32:14.070 --> 32:15.400
You can tell me about them.

32:15.400 --> 32:16.720
Let's get to know each other.

32:16.720 --> 32:18.680
Yes. I like butchering pigs.

32:18.680 --> 32:20.400
Why don't you find a pig, Your Majesty?

32:20.400 --> 32:21.530
I will be right here,

32:21.590 --> 32:22.730
deboning and butchering it,

32:22.730 --> 32:23.920
digging out its heart and lungs
for you to see.

32:23.920 --> 32:24.880
Enough, enough.

32:25.930 --> 32:27.000
I'll be direct.

32:28.000 --> 32:30.350
I intend to make you my Noble Consort.

32:30.480 --> 32:32.340
From now on, you will stay in the palace

32:32.340 --> 32:34.340
and enjoy endless wealth and glory.

32:36.400 --> 32:37.510
What a pity.

32:38.590 --> 32:40.030
I already have a husband.

32:40.640 --> 32:42.000
I cannot marry you.

32:42.480 --> 32:44.810
Didn't you say your husband went missing?

32:45.550 --> 32:47.160
He is just a husband,

32:47.160 --> 32:49.270
nothing more than a peasant
or a small vendor.

32:49.270 --> 32:50.880
How can he compare to me?

32:51.000 --> 32:52.080
Besides,

32:52.750 --> 32:54.950
is marrying you

32:54.970 --> 33:03.460
[Act with Caution]

32:55.110 --> 32:56.840
just for my own selfish desire?

32:57.110 --> 32:57.920
No!

32:58.440 --> 33:01.000
I'm doing it for the realm of Great Yin.

33:01.000 --> 33:04.930
It is to stop those treacherous officials
from controlling the court.

33:06.960 --> 33:07.830
As for you,

33:08.480 --> 33:10.510
although you are a butcher girl,

33:11.550 --> 33:13.160
I do not dislike you.

33:13.730 --> 33:14.650
Look,

33:15.000 --> 33:16.670
I have sacrificed myself for you

33:16.670 --> 33:18.070
and gone to great lengths.

33:18.070 --> 33:20.070
Can't you think of the greater good?

33:24.590 --> 33:26.680
Your Majesty, your sacrifice

33:26.920 --> 33:28.750
is for the sake of the country?

33:29.640 --> 33:30.310
Fine.

33:30.640 --> 33:32.790
I will write a divorce letter
to Xie Zheng right now.

33:32.790 --> 33:33.550
I will divorce him.

33:33.550 --> 33:34.510
Very well.

33:34.510 --> 33:35.310
Wait.

33:39.720 --> 33:41.750
Who did you say

33:41.750 --> 33:43.830
you are writing the Divorce Agreement to?

33:43.830 --> 33:45.000
Xie Zheng.

33:49.350 --> 33:50.830
Xie Jiuheng.

33:53.640 --> 33:54.840
The Marquis of Wu'an.

34:00.200 --> 34:01.660
Are you familiar with him?

34:03.340 --> 34:04.520
Yes.

34:04.450 --> 34:06.660
[Act with Caution]

34:05.030 --> 34:06.030
I know him all too well.

34:06.030 --> 34:06.890
Then I shall go.

34:06.920 --> 34:07.550
Don't!

34:13.070 --> 34:13.880
Fan.

34:14.090 --> 34:16.010
No, General Fan.

34:16.920 --> 34:18.670
Why didn't you tell me this sooner?

34:18.670 --> 34:21.199
You made me misunderstand things
for so long.

34:21.670 --> 34:24.760
The Marquis of Wu'an
is also loyal and patriotic.

34:25.360 --> 34:28.420
Marrying him is also an act
for the greater good, right?

34:29.000 --> 34:30.000
It's just that...

34:31.000 --> 34:32.310
please just pretend

34:32.429 --> 34:34.710
that today's event never happened.

34:35.090 --> 34:35.949
What do you say?

34:39.710 --> 34:40.550
Yes,

34:41.920 --> 34:43.110
Your Majesty.

35:02.160 --> 35:04.160
My Lord, Grand Tutor Tao is here.

35:05.830 --> 35:06.750
Master?

35:11.510 --> 35:12.840
You returned with the army in triumph

35:12.840 --> 35:15.000
upon the edict.

35:15.550 --> 35:17.740
This serves as a legitimate reason

35:18.030 --> 35:19.840
for you to appear in the Capital.

35:24.030 --> 35:25.190
I presume

35:27.140 --> 35:30.540
His Majesty is also part of your plan.

35:35.510 --> 35:37.320
If it weren't for the concern
that a disturbance in the court

35:37.320 --> 35:38.880
might destabilize the state,

35:38.880 --> 35:41.400
giving the Beijue people
an opportunity to take advantage,

35:41.400 --> 35:42.480
would that puppet really think

35:42.480 --> 35:44.320
he could ascend to the throne?

35:48.670 --> 35:50.670
The catastrophe 17 years ago

35:50.670 --> 35:53.400
has left the current situation
in the court

35:53.400 --> 35:55.550
tangled and complicated,

35:56.760 --> 35:58.710
with no easy solution.

35:59.490 --> 36:02.290
The lesson from 17 years ago
hasn't brought peace,

36:02.710 --> 36:05.240
but has instead
caused more turmoil to arise.

36:06.960 --> 36:09.290
It seems we've truly returned to the past.

36:10.590 --> 36:11.510
Jiuheng,

36:13.400 --> 36:14.320
entering the Capital this time

36:14.320 --> 36:17.320
means it is time for you to face Wei Yan.

36:19.150 --> 36:21.300
In this reunion of nephew and uncle,

36:21.430 --> 36:22.990
danger lurks everywhere.

36:24.110 --> 36:25.960
Are you ready?

36:28.070 --> 36:29.530
The day I enter the Capital

36:30.800 --> 36:33.060
is the anniversary of my mother's death.

36:34.070 --> 36:35.070
He and I

36:37.360 --> 36:38.360
are bound to meet.

36:58.400 --> 37:00.000
Greetings, Mother Consort.

37:00.590 --> 37:02.320
What did you

37:02.320 --> 37:03.190
ask me here for?

37:22.030 --> 37:24.030
What have you been busy with lately?

37:28.120 --> 37:29.520
Studying chess manuals.

37:29.920 --> 37:31.150
In my spare time,

37:31.400 --> 37:33.710
I also copied some
Buddhist scriptures for you.

37:33.710 --> 37:34.670
Is that all?

37:37.440 --> 37:39.340
Why has Jianjia from your palace

37:39.370 --> 37:41.500
been going to the Cold Palace so often?

37:44.360 --> 37:45.960
Perhaps she is kind-hearted

37:46.000 --> 37:47.960
and wants to give out some food.

37:49.140 --> 37:50.100
Shu.

37:57.590 --> 37:58.520
Mother Consort.

37:59.190 --> 38:00.800
I accidentally discovered that

38:00.800 --> 38:01.860
in the Cold Palace,

38:02.230 --> 38:05.560
there might be a witness
to the palace coup from 17 years ago.

38:10.320 --> 38:11.780
Who else knows about this?

38:13.110 --> 38:14.520
Only Jianjia and I.

38:14.630 --> 38:15.670
No one else.

38:16.230 --> 38:18.150
This must never be mentioned again.

38:18.150 --> 38:19.710
Pretend it never happened.

38:20.880 --> 38:22.860
The palace banquet is in 7 days.

38:23.550 --> 38:25.480
You cannot waste your prime years.

38:26.070 --> 38:27.150
You may go back.

38:27.150 --> 38:29.280
I've had the dress sent to your palace.

38:45.120 --> 38:46.050
Mother Consort.

38:46.630 --> 38:48.620
If Wei Yan is truly this audacious,

38:48.960 --> 38:50.920
we should uncover the truth
from 17 years ago,

38:50.920 --> 38:52.320
execute his entire clan,

38:52.400 --> 38:55.260
and reclaim imperial power from him,
shouldn't we?

38:57.070 --> 38:58.480
Why are you and my brother

38:58.840 --> 39:01.000
so afraid of him?

39:08.360 --> 39:11.320
A life of luxury has made you so naive.

39:12.020 --> 39:14.530
Do you think Wei Yan
is that easy to defeat?

39:15.030 --> 39:16.480
I survived these 17 years of suffering

39:16.480 --> 39:17.360
because I've been cautious

39:17.360 --> 39:19.360
and enduring humiliation.

39:20.320 --> 39:22.000
If you care about me at all,

39:22.190 --> 39:23.190
listen to me.

39:23.190 --> 39:24.990
Stop meddling in this, alright?

39:28.760 --> 39:29.590
Shu.

39:36.870 --> 39:37.620
Yes.

39:38.280 --> 39:39.230
I see.

39:46.400 --> 39:47.460
I'll take my leave.

39:53.800 --> 39:55.200
For some unknown reason,

39:55.880 --> 39:57.000
I feel...

39:58.230 --> 39:59.360
so uneasy.

40:00.480 --> 40:02.400
Just like 17 years ago.

40:03.900 --> 40:06.870
[Where Compassion and Grace Meet]

40:06.030 --> 40:07.030
Your Majesty.

40:07.190 --> 40:09.190
The Marquis of Wu'an has led his troops

40:09.190 --> 40:11.050
to the outskirts of the Capital.

40:11.110 --> 40:12.110
In three days,

40:12.400 --> 40:14.280
he will enter the city as decreed.

40:17.880 --> 40:20.360
That is earlier than I anticipated.

40:21.190 --> 40:22.710
Could it be that he found out

40:22.710 --> 40:24.030
I have designs on Fan Changyu,

40:24.030 --> 40:25.760
so he came to the Capital early?

40:27.800 --> 40:29.230
He really has wild ambitions!

40:29.230 --> 40:30.110
Yes.

40:30.150 --> 40:31.480
A mere butcher girl,

40:31.480 --> 40:32.840
and the Marquis of Wu'an
wants to fight me for her?

40:32.840 --> 40:33.590
Yes, yes!

40:33.590 --> 40:34.760
Tell me, why is my life

40:34.760 --> 40:36.400
-so miserable?
-Yes!

40:36.400 --> 40:38.440
No, no, no! It's not miserable.

40:43.670 --> 40:45.280
Prime Minister Wei is a powerful official,

40:45.280 --> 40:46.230
and the Grand Tutor is as slippery
as an eel.

40:46.230 --> 40:47.150
An eel.

40:47.550 --> 40:48.510
I finally found

40:48.510 --> 40:50.760
a village woman I could easily manipulate.

40:50.760 --> 40:51.590
But now she has become...

40:51.590 --> 40:53.250
She has become a Marchioness!

40:57.150 --> 40:59.280
If the Jizhou Army and the Yanzhou Army

40:59.400 --> 41:00.630
were to unite,

41:02.630 --> 41:05.000
wouldn't that create
another Lord Changxin?

41:05.000 --> 41:05.800
Well...

41:07.190 --> 41:08.480
No, no.

41:09.550 --> 41:11.210
I cannot let them join forces.

41:13.630 --> 41:14.280
Also...

41:15.110 --> 41:16.400
That damned grandson
of the former Eastern Palace—

41:16.400 --> 41:17.480
where is he now?

41:18.320 --> 41:19.070
Your Majesty,

41:19.070 --> 41:21.630
there is still no news about him.

41:21.630 --> 41:23.070
And in recent days,

41:23.070 --> 41:25.110
Prime Minister Wei
has been acting as usual,

41:25.110 --> 41:26.640
with no strange movements.

41:28.000 --> 41:28.710
You!

41:28.710 --> 41:30.380
This is all your fault!

41:31.030 --> 41:31.630
Come back!

41:37.920 --> 41:40.180
I cannot just sit here and wait for death.

41:44.780 --> 41:46.540
Hurry up and summon Grand Tutor Li.

41:46.540 --> 41:47.230
-Yes.
-Summon Grand Tutor Li.

41:47.230 --> 41:48.960
Yes. I will go right away.

41:49.360 --> 41:50.150
Hurry up!

41:50.510 --> 41:53.630
Servants! Summon Grand Tutor Li
for an audience!

41:57.710 --> 42:00.860
[Speak with Caution]

41:58.760 --> 42:00.220
Greetings, Your Majesty.

42:02.920 --> 42:04.920
Recently, the rumor about the grandson
of the former Eastern Palace

42:04.920 --> 42:06.850
has been spreading like wildfire.

42:06.960 --> 42:07.880
Grand Tutor Li,

42:08.110 --> 42:09.960
what is your opinion on this?

42:10.630 --> 42:11.440
Your Majesty,

42:12.030 --> 42:14.030
this rumor is difficult to verify.

42:14.440 --> 42:16.150
But at such a critical moment,

42:16.150 --> 42:17.750
for it to suddenly emerge...

42:18.230 --> 42:19.480
In my opinion,

42:19.760 --> 42:22.220
someone must be
plotting behind the scenes,

42:22.360 --> 42:23.710
adding fuel to the fire.

42:25.710 --> 42:27.320
I was thinking the same.

42:28.760 --> 42:30.110
Do you...

42:30.110 --> 42:31.960
have any suspects in mind?

42:32.400 --> 42:33.230
Your Majesty,

42:33.590 --> 42:36.320
the Marquis of Wu'an
holds heavy military power.

42:36.510 --> 42:39.840
His army is openly camped
outside the Capital.

42:39.840 --> 42:42.480
His wild ambition is as clear as day.

42:44.550 --> 42:46.880
I venture to suggest

42:47.230 --> 42:48.590
that we act decisively

42:49.510 --> 42:52.440
and uproot this hidden danger.

42:56.280 --> 42:57.070
No.

42:57.670 --> 42:58.400
No.

42:59.880 --> 43:00.670
No.

43:03.840 --> 43:04.840
If we do that,

43:05.230 --> 43:07.230
won't we offend Prime Minister Wei?

43:07.480 --> 43:09.880
Your Majesty, I have a plan

43:10.000 --> 43:13.150
to help you accomplish this.

43:16.330 --> 43:18.840
I heard there is news in the Cold Palace

43:18.840 --> 43:20.920
about the late Consort Shu's
personal maid.
